Class GetOperationResult<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.fasterxml.clustermate.client.operation.OperationResult<T>

  • Type Parameters:
    T - Result type of GetContentProcessor

    public class GetOperationResult<T>
extends OperationResultImpl<GetOperationResult<T>>
    OperationResult subtype used with GET operations, adds actual result (of type T which is type of GetContentProcessor passed to call).

        Simple accessor for checking whether call succeeded well enough that we may consider it full success. We may either choose to do more updates (if nodes are available); up to OperationResultImpl.succeededMaximally() level; or just return and declare success.
